
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Index";
    Layout = "~/Pages/Shared/_Layout.cshtml";
}

<style>
    /* Add your custom styles here */
    .icon i {
        font-size: 36px; /* Adjust icon size as needed */
    }
</style>

<section class="service">
    <div class="container">
        <h2 class="service-heading textGradient">Our Services</h2>
        <div class="row">
            <!-- Service 1: Manual Therapy -->
            <div class="col-lg-4">
                <div class="icon">
                    <!-- Icon for Manual Therapy -->
                    <i class="fas fa-hand-paper"></i>
                </div>
                <h3 class="textGradient">Manual Therapy</h3>
                <p>Our skilled physiotherapist utilize hands-on techniques to assess, diagnose, and treat musculoskeletal conditions. Manual therapy techniques such as joint mobilization, soft tissue massage, and manipulation aim to reduce pain, improve joint mobility, and enhance tissue healing.</p>
            </div>

            <!-- Service 2: Exercise Rehabilitation -->
            <div class="col-lg-4">
                <div class="icon">
                    <!-- Icon for Exercise Rehabilitation -->
                    <i class="fas fa-dumbbell"></i>
                </div>
                <h3 class="textGradient">Exercise Rehabilitation</h3>
                <p>We believe in the power of exercise to promote recovery and enhance physical function. Our team will design a customized exercise program to address your specific goals and needs. Through therapeutic exercises, we aim to improve strength, flexibility, endurance, and overall functional capacity.</p>
            </div>

            <!-- Service 3: Electrotherapy -->
            <div class="col-lg-4">
                <div class="icon">
                    <!-- Icon for Electrotherapy -->
                    <i class="fas fa-bolt"></i>
                </div>
                <h3 class="textGradient">Electrotherapy</h3>
                <p>Electrotherapy modalities, such as ultrasound, electrical stimulation, and laser therapy, can be effective in pain management, reducing inflammation, promoting tissue healing, and improving circulation. Our therapists will determine the most suitable electrotherapy treatment for your condition.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Service 4: Acupuncture -->
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-lg-4">
                <div class="icon">
                    <i class="fas fa-leaf"></i> <!-- Icon for Acupuncture -->
                </div>
                <h3 class="textGradient">Acupuncture</h3>
                <p>Our certified acupuncturist provide acupuncture treatments to help alleviate pain, restore balance, and promote overall well-being. Acupuncture involves the insertion of thin needles into specific points on the body, stimulating the body’s natural healing response.</p>
            </div>

            <!-- Service 5: Postural Assessment and Correction -->
            <div class="col-lg-4">
                <div class="icon">
                    <i class="fas fa-ruler-horizontal"></i> <!-- Icon for Postural Assessment and Correction -->
                </div>
                <h3 class="textGradient">Postural Assessment and Correction</h3>
                <p>Poor posture can contribute to various musculoskeletal issues. Our physiotherapist will conduct a thorough postural assessment to identify any imbalances or abnormalities. We will then develop a tailored treatment plan, including postural correction exercises and ergonomic advice to improve your posture and prevent further problems.</p>
            </div>

            <!-- Service 6: Sports Injury Rehabilitation -->
            <div class="col-lg-4">
                <div class="icon">
                    <i class="fas fa-running"></i> <!-- Icon for Sports Injury Rehabilitation -->
                </div>
                <h3 class="textGradient">Sports Injury Rehabilitation</h3>
                <p>If you have sustained a sports-related injury, our specialized sports physiotherapy team is here to help you recover and get back to your active lifestyle. We provide targeted treatment plans, including manual therapy, therapeutic exercises, and sports-specific training, to optimize your rehabilitation and prevent future injuries.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Service 7: Pain Management -->
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-lg-4">
                <div class="icon">
                    <i class="fas fa-heartbeat"></i> <!-- Icon for Pain Management -->
                </div>
                <h3 class="textGradient">Pain Management</h3>
                <p>Chronic pain can significantly impact your quality of life. Our physiotherapist employ various techniques, such as manual therapy, therapeutic exercises, electrotherapy, and pain education, to manage and reduce pain levels. We aim to improve your overall well-being and restore your ability to engage in daily activities.</p>
            </div>

            <!-- Service 8: Geriatric Physiotherapy -->
            <div class="col-lg-4">
                <div class="icon">
                    <i class="fas fa-user-friends"></i> <!-- Icon for Geriatric Physiotherapy -->
                </div>
                <h3 class="textGradient">Geriatric Physiotherapy</h3>
                <p>We offer specialized physiotherapy services for older adults to address age-related conditions, improve mobility, and enhance independence. Our geriatric physiotherapy treatments focus on fall prevention, improving balance, managing arthritis, and maintaining functional abilities for a healthier and more active lifestyle.</p>
            </div>

            <!-- Service 9: Joint Injury -->
            <div class="col-lg-4">
                <div class="icon">
                    <i class="fas fa-bone"></i> <!-- Icon for Joint Injury -->
                </div>
                <h3 class="textGradient">Joint Injury</h3>
                <p>Specialized care for joint injuries, including rehabilitation and pain management. Our team of experts will create a tailored treatment plan to help you recover from joint injuries, regain mobility, and alleviate pain, allowing you to return to your daily activities.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Service 10: Manual Therapy -->
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-lg-4">
                <div class="icon">
                    <i class="fas fa-microscope"></i> <!-- Icon for Microscopic Examination -->
                </div>
                <h3 class="textGradient">Microscopic Examination</h3>
                <p>We offer microscopic examination services to provide detailed analysis and diagnosis of various musculoskeletal conditions. Our advanced equipment and expertise ensure accurate results, guiding personalized treatment plans for optimal recovery.</p>
            </div>

            <!-- Service 11: Massage Therapy -->
            <div class="col-lg-4">
                <div class="icon">
                    <i class="fas fa-spa"></i> <!-- Icon for Massage Therapy -->
                </div>
                <h3 class="textGradient">Massage Therapy</h3>
                <p>Our experienced massage therapists offer a range of therapeutic massage techniques to relieve muscle tension, reduce stress, and promote relaxation. Whether you need deep tissue massage, Swedish massage, or sports massage, we tailor our approach to your specific needs.</p>
            </div>

            <!-- Service 12: Orthopedic Surgery -->
            <div class="col-lg-4">
                <div class="icon">
                    <i class="fas fa-user-md"></i> <!-- Icon for Orthopedic Surgery -->
                </div>
                <h3 class="textGradient">Orthopedic Surgery</h3>
                <p>For complex musculoskeletal conditions requiring surgical intervention, our skilled orthopedic surgeons provide comprehensive care. From joint replacements to arthroscopic procedures, we aim to restore function and mobility, ensuring the best possible outcomes for our patients.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>




